to the editor re on doomed flight passengers vowed to perish fighting front page sept 13 i am particularly moved by the actions of those aboard united airlines flight 93 who in the face of certain death took quick action and successfully avoided having their aircraft possibly become the fourth airborne bomb on tuesday the memory of their sacrifice will remain with me for the rest of my life i hope that their bravery will provide some solace to their survivors fran menzel middletown nj sept 13 2001

